# Forecast API

API FastAPI para forecasting por municipioĂ—sector.

## Endpoints
- GET /health  -> estado
- POST /run-forecast -> ejecuta pipeline

## Variables de entorno
- SCM_DO_BUILD_DURING_DEPLOYMENT=1
- WEBSITES_PORT=8000
- (otras: TENANT_ID, CLIENT_ID, CLIENT_SECRET, SHAREPOINT_SITE, etc.)

## Run local
pip install -r requirements.txt
uvicorn main:app --host 0.0.0.0 --port 8000

